= Brite

== The BrightLite of Website Tools

* http://proutils.rubyforge.org
* http://proutils.rubyforge.org/brite


== DESCRIPTION

Brite is a static website/blog generation tool.
It is very easy to use, and borrows best-of-breed
ideas from a number of similar projects.


== FEATURES/ISSUES

* Awesome
* Extra Cool
* And Dyn-o-mite!


== RELEASE NOTES

Please see the HISTORY file.


== SYNOPSIS

Give me some time...


== HOW TO INSTALL

You know the routine.

  gem install brite

If you're old fashion and want to install to a site
location, use Setup.rb (http://setup.rubyforge.org).


